  "content": [
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Nal stands, and the floating disk which was hovering before her\nsettles gently to the ground."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"As you know, Elder Thrush depends on me to communicate\ntelepathically with Rangers in the field, but to do so effectively, I\nrequire the support of the most powerful spirits of this land. One of\nthose, interestingly enough, is the spirit of the Verdessa. It shares a\ndeep connection with the spirit of the Valley\u2014like a mother to her\nchild\u2014and for some reason, I cannot reach it. It's very distressing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\"I've received word that a wandering botanist has recently returned\nfrom an excursion to the Verdessa, and that she's brought some\nrare plant specimens along with her. She is currently staying at the\nmerchant's quarters in Kobo's Market. If I had one of these specimens,\nI may be able to use it to reconnect with the spirit of the Verdessa.\nPerhaps you could accompany me to the market? I would be very\ngrateful.\""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "h4",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Rangers Choose"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [],
          "id": null,
